# AFL Data Analysis Project

## Overview
This project analyzes AFL match and player data using SQL Server and Power BI.

## Tools Used
- SQL Server (data cleaning and transformation)
- Power BI (data visualization and dashboard)

## Data Model
- Teams
- Players
- Matches
- Player Statistics

## Key Features
- KPI overview (Total Matches, Teams, Players, Goals)
- Top 5 teams by wins, goals, and tackles
- Top 5 players by goals, tackles, and performance
- Venue-based analysis
- Interactive filters (Team and Venue)

## Key Insights
- High-scoring teams are not always the most successful in terms of wins
- A small number of players dominate performance metrics
- Venue has an impact on scoring trends

